title: Found: Sunnybank Hills girl, 12, had not been seen since Saturday oct 24 |
text:
Police had called for public assistance to locate the girl who had been reported missing from Sunnybank Hills.
The girl was last seen at her home address at Sunnybank Hills on Saturday morning.
